description: In this video, I show you how to make my most favourite vegan cheese ever: my vegan cranberry & thyme cheese ball. This easy vegan cheese recipe is so insanely delicious but only requires 9 ingredients to make. You can make it ahead of time making this vegan cheese ball perfect for a party appetizer. I've had people try this and think it was cows milk cheese, it's that good. I hope you guys love this recipe for the best vegan cheese ever!!! :) Disclaimer: This video description contains affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases
